						<summary>

						<p>This records the repair to the tank-bund which is said to have been built by one Mummuḍiśōḻa-Siṅgaḷāntaka-Muttaraiyaṉ and destroyed by breach some time afterwards. The repair was effected by Periyāṉ Kulōttuṅgaśōḻa-Kaṉakarājaṉ, the headman of Koṭṭiyūr in Kāṉa-nāḍu.</p>						

						</summary>
